KAME instllation notes

KAME needs following libraries:
kdelibs and others depending on kdelibs
boost
ruby
gsl
fftw (ver.3)
ftgl
lapack/atlas/blas
linux-gpib (optional)
National Instruments DAQmx library (optional)
mikachanfont (included in source tree)

The document files and the font file of mikachanfont has to be copied to (root-source)/kame/mikachanfont

To build KAME
cmake (options) (path_to_source_dir)
make
su -c 'make install'
